storyInfo: 'The Great Aquapit' will soon be demolished, bringing the gang here for one last round of fun. The Durins look forward to the birth of their next landmark, while Inam and Gavial discuss Acahualla's future.

attributes.content: With the results of the referendum, the Great Aquapit will soon complete its historic half-year mission. It will be blown up and turned into construction material once again.
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: Citizens, I'm afraid this slightly extended summer carnival will soon come to an end.
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: *sobs*... I'll always remember our beautiful time together forever.
attributes.name: Durin

attributes.content: But the super slide is so much fun, you can't get enough of it! I never thought we'd have to say goodbye...
attributes.name: Durin

attributes.content: However! In the Great Aquapit's place, we'll have an all-new, prettier, and completely different structure! After all, this is Zeruertza, a city built by the best architectural designers!
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: Stitch Canvas and Catch Lightrace are two awe-inspiring, up-and-coming architectural designers. Over the next few months, the two of them will submit their design proposals...
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: Imagine the show showdown they have in store for us.
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: Hehe, this brings me back to the dome design contest they had a few years ago, when they just made their debuts!
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: The duel ended all those years ago without a winner, but who will win the right to design Zeruertza's next landmark? Let usâ€”
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: Let me get a sip of water first.
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: Croque, I've never seen you so enthusiastic. Have you been drinking?
attributes.name: Edge Eartheart

attributes.content: No. Not yet, at least.
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: Now this isn't like you at all.
attributes.name: Edge Eartheart

attributes.content: I was watching videos of a competition on the surface that I got from Inam, and it seems they have a role called 'the MC'.
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: I thought I might dip into a new career path.
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: Anyhow! Although the architects' designs are yet to come, my fellow citizens, the tail end of our summer is going to be a fleeting one!
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: Before the slide is blown up, let us enjoy it all we can!
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: Ohhhh!
attributes.name: Durin

attributes.content: Gavial!
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Tomimi, watch out! Slow down!
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: I was so, so jealous when I heard you guys went to the waterfall in Acahualla!
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Hehe, and this time I get to join in on the fun!
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: You're such a kid.
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: Hm? What's wrong? You're usually so careful to hide your tail. Let's see... Did it get thicker again?
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: Eh? Nope, not even a little! I checked with a measuring tape before I got here! It's been months since I got any thicker!
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Oh? Sounds like you're really hung up on it.
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: Waaaahhh... Eat my water blast!
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Heh, you little runt! It's on!
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: They're more like Durins than you are.
attributes.name: Avdotya

attributes.content: How would you know what it means to be 'Durin', Lupo?
attributes.name: Stitch Canvas

attributes.content: You seem a little nervous. Are you worried about your contest with Catch?
attributes.name: Avdotya

attributes.content: Worried? Over him? Don't make me laugh. I haven't fallen so low. It's just laypeople tend to like his proposals more.
attributes.name: Stitch Canvas

attributes.content: Mine get their fair share of fans, too. Perhaps I should be bringing something different to the table. That's how I'll win.
attributes.name: Stitch Canvas

attributes.content: Perhaps I should just... *sigh*! I should probably take my mind off of that right now.
attributes.name: Stitch Canvas

attributes.content: To tell the truth... if we don't care about aesthetics and just look at how fun it is, this 'Great Aquapit' isn't so bad.
attributes.name: Stitch Canvas

attributes.content: Oh, so you enjoy these things, too?
attributes.name: Avdotya

attributes.content: Every now and then.
attributes.name: Stitch Canvas

attributes.content: Stitch, you're here!
attributes.name: Catch Lightrace

attributes.content: Want to try out the slide with the downstream speed set to max? It wears the equipment out, so we don't usually get to do it.
attributes.name: Catch Lightrace

attributes.content: I just tried it a couple times with Elysium. It was amazingly fast!
attributes.name: Catch Lightrace

attributes.content: It does hurt a little when you hit the water, though. Still, wanna try?
attributes.name: Catch Lightrace

attributes.content: No, thanks. I'm not one bit interested in fun and games like...
attributes.name: Stitch Canvas

attributes.content: Whooo! Bombs away!
attributes.name: Elysium

attributes.content: Catch, my brother! This impact force is on another level! Did you see how high that splash went?!
attributes.name: Elysium

attributes.content: Maybe we should try something different. Say... see which of us can land with the tiniest splash?
attributes.name: Catch Lightrace

attributes.content: Keep the splashes small? Good idea! Sounds like it won't hurt nearly as bad.
attributes.name: Elysium

attributes.content: My sand castle...
attributes.name: Stitch Canvas

attributes.content: (Hey, uh, Catch, did we perhaps... screw up?)
attributes.name: Elysium

attributes.content: (Uh, even though this is Stitch we're talking about, he can't possibly be mad over a sand castle, right?)
attributes.name: Catch Lightrace

attributes.content: (He seems rather angry to me, though.)
attributes.name: Elysium

attributes.content: (In that case, we should probably...)
attributes.name: Catch Lightrace

attributes.content: Hey, where are you two going? You're just going to run? Get back here!
attributes.name: Stitch Canvas

attributes.content: Yep, you did very well getting everyone going.
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: I have your video tapes to thank. That's where I picked it up.
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: Next, we can hold a series of contests to keep the enthusiasm that goes with this 'championship' contest going, then we'll use Catch and Stitch's design contest in a few months to pump everyone up to the max.
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: We could print some paper slips for the audience to use to show their support for one side, with prizes given to those who pick the right side.
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: We call those lottery tickets. You're really good at picking things up. Up on the surface, there are merchants who line their pockets by selling them.
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: We Durins don't much care for money in that way... Let's have the losing side pay for the winners' drinks for a month!
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: Hm, we could make it two months to make things more exciting, too. We'll have to decide with a referendum.
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: Later on, perhaps we could issue some more lottery tickets covering how many months' worth of alcohol are owed in the end.
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: I'm starting to worry about the Zeruertzans' future.
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: Hm, I'm not used to feeling unhelpful.
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: What's wrong? Do you have to beat something up to satisfy yourself?
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Not really.
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: Still, if this goes well, Acahualla will get its hands on some Durin. Would've been a totally pointless trip otherwise.
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: Gavial may have left home a long time ago, but she actually really cares about Acahualla!
attributes.name: Tomimi

attributes.content: Yeah, I've been to so many different places, but the rainforest is the one place where I feel most at home.
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: Are you going to come back, then?
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: Not planning on it. Not yet, at least. I still have lots of patients to take care of back at Rhodes Island.
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: There are plenty of Tiacauh who want you to go back. You could think about becoming their lord ameer, even.
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: Yeah, and they want bananas to sprout straight out of the soil, too. Can't always get what you want.
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: Gavial, you would be the most fitting lord ameer for Acahualla. You are the only one who can rein in each and every Tiacauh.
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: Everyone is awaiting your return.
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: And if you simply cannot do it, then it's ultimately likely... that a lord ameer from the Court of Sargon will come to govern Acahualla instead.
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: And when that happens, Acahualla will no longer be the free land you knew.
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: But don't we already have you for our Great Chief?
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: There are some things I can't do anything about.
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: I can come up with ideas to help get us in better shape, but I'm not the one who can really bring the Tiacauh together.
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: It's not like I'm running away from responsibility here, Inam.
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: It's just... I haven't thought through how to actually do it.
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: You know how to think? Color me surprised.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Hey, Zumama, you picking a fight?!
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: What I'm saying is, you usually do stuff without thinking.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: And that's fine when it's just me, but this is about all those Tiacauh...
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: All good things must come to an end. Isn't that right? So this giant slide will be torn down for something new.
attributes.name: Catch Lightrace

attributes.content: I actually didn't catch much of what you were talking about. All I want to say is, my friends, let me get a picture of all of you together while it's still standing.
attributes.name: Catch Lightrace

attributes.content: Haha, alright, let's toss all this complicated stuff aside for now.
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: Right now, we gotta have fun!
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: Tomimi, you gimme a smile, too!
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: Looks like you've mastered the Durin philosophy.
attributes.name: Catch Lightrace

attributes.content: Well, it's not often we get a vacation. As if I'm gonna waste it!
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: Well said! Here's to you! How about some berry tomato wine? It's on me.
attributes.name: Catch Lightrace

attributes.content: Nah, I'll have to pass on that.
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.text: The demolition explosives have already been set, and the assistant robots have made all the preparations.
Soon, the big water slide that has brought everyone so much joy will be gone without a trace.
But summer must come to an end, and there will no doubt be greater fun in the future.
That's what all the Zeruertzans believe.
The explosion isn't nearly as loud as anyone expects. The slide simply slowly disintegrates.
Or perhaps, a little more poetically, it melts into the water.

attributes.content: My, what a graceful way to disappear.
attributes.name: Elysium

attributes.content: Here I thought you would pass out from all that drink and miss the demolition.
attributes.name: Stitch Canvas

attributes.content: Haha, I know how to have a good time.
attributes.name: Elysium

attributes.content: Though, at times like these, I generally keep myself clearheaded.
attributes.name: Elysium

attributes.content: That's the most basic respect I have for things as they fade away.
attributes.name: Elysium

attributes.content: Whoa, were you actually a secret genius? That would be such a cheap cliche, even in the Zeruertzan library.
attributes.name: Stitch Canvas

attributes.content: Oh, you little rascal!
attributes.name: Elysium

attributes.content: Stitch.
attributes.name: Catch Lightrace

attributes.content: Catch...
attributes.name: Stitch Canvas

attributes.content: It's time we got serious. Let's both do our best, fair and square.
attributes.name: Catch Lightrace

attributes.content: Shake hands if you agree?
attributes.name: Catch Lightrace

attributes.content: Alright... Out of the most basic respect for another Zeruertzan.
attributes.name: Stitch Canvas

attributes.content: Say, you two actually get along pretty well, don't you?
attributes.name: Elysium

attributes.content: What, are you blind?! Where'd you get that idea?
attributes.name: Stitch Canvas

attributes.content: Now, things are going to get real from here on out!
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: Has Croque been drinking...?
attributes.name: Stitch Canvas

attributes.content: The warm-up of warm-ups, the prelude to preludes! The first season of the Zeruertza Competition Series!
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: *Drumroll*â€”Ta-dah! A swimming contest!
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface

attributes.content: How about it?
attributes.name: Croque Diamondface
